Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlan WKL NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL NL') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpen WKL NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL NL') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenCritical WKL NL
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL NL') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL NL

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanAssignedToCurrentUser WKL NL

Data.name: MPTTestExecsAndTestsInTestPlanNoFixVer WKL NL
